export const groupingMap = [
    {
        label: "Primary",
        color: "primary",
        colspan: 0,
        columns: [
            {
                id: "region",
                data: "REGION",
                label: "Region",
                type: "dropdown",
                mandatory: true,
                manually: true,
                width: 100

            {
                data: "NAME",
                label: "Name",
                type: "text",
                readonly: true,
                mandatory: true,
                manually: false,
                width: 100

            {
                id: "etat",

                type: "dropdown",

                mandatory: true,
                manually: true,
                width: 110

                data: "ARCHIVED",

            {

            {

            {
                id: "dateIng",

                width: 100

            {
                id: "siteTechnology",
                data: "SITETECHNOLOGY",

                type: "dropdown",
                mandatory: true,
                manually: true,
                width: 120
            },
        ]
    },
    {
        label: "Information",
        color: "info",
        colspan: 0,
        columns: [
            {
                data: "COMMENTS",
                label: "Comments",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 100

        ]
    },
    {
        label: "Microwave Part",
        color: "info",
        colspan: 0,
        columns: [
            {
                id: "sVlan",
                data: "SVLAN",
                label: "SVLAN",
                type: "numeric",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 100
            },
            {
                id: "techMwSite",
                data: "TECHMWSITE",
                label: "TECH MW SITE",
                type: "dropdown",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 150
            },
            {
                id: "mwEquip",
                data: "MWEQUIP",
                label: "MW Equipment",
                type: "dropdown",
                source: [],
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 250
            },
            {
                id: "mwPort",

                type: "dropdown",

                width: 150
            },
            {
                id: "technoMwAggre",

                width: 150

                width: 150
            },

                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,

                width: 150

                label: "SDH AGGRE Equipment",
                type: "text",

                manually: true,
                width: 150
            },
            {

                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 150
            },
        ]
    },
    {
        label: "FO Part",
        color: "radio",
        colspan: 0,
        columns: [
            {
                id: "ticketNumber",
                data: "TICKETNUMBER",
                label: "Ticket Number",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 150
            },
            {
                id: "portSite",
                data: "PORTSITE",
                label: "PORT SITE",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 150
            },
            {
                id: "portAggre",

                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 150

            {

                label: "IP EQUIPMENT",
                type: "dropdown",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 150

            {

                label: "IP PORT",
                type: "dropdown",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 150

            {

                manually: true,
                width: 150

            {
                data: "BOARDTYPE",
                label: "Board Type",
                type: "dropdown",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 150
            },
            {
                data: "OM",
                label: "O&M",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 120
            },
            {
                data: "NBIP",
                label: "NB IP",
                type: "text",
                validator: "ipValidator",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 120
            },
            {
                data: "GW",
                label: "GW",
                type: "text",
                //validator: "ipValidator",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 120
            },
            {
                data: "MASK",
                label: "Mask",
                validator: "ipValidator",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 120
            },
            {
                data: "2emeIp",
                label: "2eme IP",
                validator: "ipValidator",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 110
            },
            {
                data: "NTPIP",
